Overview:
PosAbility provides quality educational and psychological services to school aged children and adolescents, implementing positive approaches to maximize a child’s ability to; 

· learn to their highest potential; 
· live life to the full with confidence and; 
· grow to be all they can be. 

A range of assessments, educational and counselling services aim to help children and their parents to discover, focus on and learn how to use their strengths in all areas of their lives; thus maximizing their educational and social outcomes and therefore enhancing their emotional wellbeing.
